## Architecture

```text
+------------+
|  Customer  |
+------------+
       |
       v
+---------------+
| API Gateway   |
+---------------+
       |
       v
+----------------------+
| CreateOrder Lambda   |
+----------------------+
       |                    \
       |                     \
       v                      v
+---------------+      +---------------+
| DynamoDB      |      | Amazon SQS    |
| Store Order   |      +---------------+
+---------------+              |
                               v
                    +----------------------+
                    | OrderProcessor Lambda|
                    +----------------------+
                          |            |
                          |            |
                          v            v
                 +---------------+  +-------------+
                 | DynamoDB      |  | Amazon SNS  |
                 | CONFIRMED     |  | Email       |
                 +---------------+  +-------------+
```
